I"ö7<h1 id="sentiment-analysis-for-arabizi-on-social-media">Sentiment Analysis for Arabizi on Social Media</h1>

<p>Author: <a href="https://tahatobaili.github.io/" target="_blank">Taha Tobaili</a>, <a href="http://kmi.open.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Knowledge Media Institute (KMi)</a>.<br />
Supervisors: <a href="http://people.kmi.open.ac.uk/miriam-fernandez/" target="_blank">Miriam Fernandez</a> and <a href="http://people.kmi.open.ac.uk/harith/" target="_blank">Harith Alani</a>, KMi.<br />
Sytem Developer: <a href="http://kmi.open.ac.uk/people/member/chris-sanders" target="_blank">Chris Sanders</a>, KMi.<br />
Acknowledgments: <a href="https://sas.lau.edu.lb/csm/people/sanaa-sharafeddine.php" target="_blank">Sanaa Sharafeddine</a>, <a href="https://people.epfl.ch/rania.islambouli?lang=en" target="_blank">Rania Islambuli</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/omar-farhat-2aa689102/" target="_blank">Omar Farhat</a>, and
